sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_007_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Regular Start Charging Session – Cached Id
    Note over CP,CS: Table 127, Section 3.3.1, p.113

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver plugs in the cable.]

    CP->>CS: 1. StatusNotification.req
    Note over CP: Tool validation (Step 1):<br/>status is Preparing
    CS-->>CP: 2. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: [EV driver presents identification.]

    CP->>CS: 3. StartTransaction.req
    CS-->>CP: 4. StartTransaction.conf
    Note over CS: SUT validation (Step 4):<br/>idTagInfo.status is Accepted

    CP->>CS: 5. StatusNotification.req
    Note over CP: Tool validation (Step 5):<br/>status is Charging
    CS-->>CP: 6. StatusNotification.conf
